text: Check out ngrok.io. It creates a tunnel with any open ports - so if you run a dash app, or train tensorflow on google cloud or whatever, you can just run ngrok then access the url from anywhere. Works well for Tensorboard, Dash, etc. So you dont have to run a full webserver with apache
